<lb n="1068c03" ed="T"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="1068c04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1068c05" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 2163</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="1068c06" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"></cb:mulu><note n="1068001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，常曉和尚請來＝法琳寺常曉律師【甲】，〔常曉…錄〕八字－【丙】</note><note n="1068001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，〔常曉和尚請來目錄〕八字－【丙】，常曉和尚請來＝法琳寺常曉律師【甲】</note><cb:jhead><app n="1068001"><lem wit="【大】">常曉和尚請來目錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">法琳寺常曉律師目錄</rdg></app><note n="1068001" type="rest" place="foot">【原】鎌倉時代寫高山寺藏本，【甲】享保二年寫大谷大學藏本，【乙】大日本佛教全書，【丙】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="1068c07" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1068c08" ed="T"/><cb:div type="xu"><cb:mulu level="1" type="序">上表</cb:mulu><p xml:id="pT55p1068c0801">入唐學法沙門常曉言。常曉以去承和三年
<lb n="1068c09" ed="T"/>五月。銜命留學遠期萬里之外。其年漂迴。四
<lb n="1068c10" ed="T"/>年亦不果渡海。五年六月進發。同年八月到
<lb n="1068c11" ed="T"/>淮南城廣<note n="1068002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綾＝凌【丙】</note><app n="1068002"><lem wit="【大】">綾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">凌</rdg></app>舘安置。孟冬使等入朝。常曉不
<lb n="1068c12" ed="T"/>得隨使入京。<note n="1068003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1068003"><lem wit="【大】">徒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">從</rdg></app>留<note n="1068004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（綾）＋舘【甲】</note><app n="1068004"><lem wit="【大】">舘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">綾舘</rdg></app>裏。空經多日。至于
<lb n="1068c13" ed="T"/>歲盡勅命未有<note n="1068005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">爰＝受【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1068005"><lem wit="【大】">爰</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">受</rdg></app>。則周遊郡內訪擇師依。幸
<lb n="1068c14" ed="T"/>遇栖靈寺灌頂阿闍梨法號文㻮和尚。并華
<lb n="1068c15" ed="T"/>林寺三教講論大德元照座主。其文㻮和尚
<lb n="1068c16" ed="T"/>則不空三藏弟子。兼<note n="1068006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔惠〕－【甲】</note><app n="1068006"><lem wit="【大】">惠</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>應阿闍梨付法人也。
<lb n="1068c17" ed="T"/>妙鉤經律深通密藏。法之棟<note n="1068007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">梁＝樑【丙】</note><app n="1068007"><lem wit="【大】">梁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">樑</rdg></app>。國之所歸。
<lb n="1068c18" ed="T"/>同年臘月。請節度使處分。配住栖靈寺。文㻮
<lb n="1068c19" ed="T"/>和尚以為師主。始學法儀。兼往花林寺。元照
<lb n="1068c20" ed="T"/>座主邊問本宗義。并得文書也。然大師尚佛
<lb n="1068c21" ed="T"/>法之流<note n="1068008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">轉＝傳ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1068008"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">轉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">傳</rdg></app>。歎生民之可拔。授我以金剛大
<lb n="1068c22" ed="T"/>法。許我以阿闍梨位也。膝步<note n="1068009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（如）＋知【甲】</note><app n="1068009"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">如知</rdg></app>未知。接足
<lb n="1068c23" ed="T"/>得<note n="1068010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">不＝未ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1068010"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">未</rdg></app>得。幸賴國家之大造大師之慈悲。學金
<lb n="1068c24" ed="T"/>剛<note n="1068011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔海〕－ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1068011"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">海</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>瑜伽。習<note n="1068012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝太【甲】＊</note><app n="1068012"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">太</rdg></app>元帥祕法。斯法也則如來
<lb n="1068c25" ed="T"/>之肝心。眾生之父母。於國城塹。於人筋脈。是
<lb n="1068c26" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#1068012"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">太</rdg></app>元帥者。<note n="1068013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">都＋（教）【甲】</note><app n="1068013"><lem wit="【大】">都</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">都教</rdg></app>內不傳於十供奉以外。諸州
<lb n="1068c27" ed="T"/>無出於節度<note n="1068014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔使〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1068014"><lem wit="【大】">使</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>宅。以表緣其靈驗不可思議
<lb n="1068c28" ed="T"/>也。諸佛菩薩金剛天等像雖在前來。此像未
<lb n="1068c29" ed="T"/>曾請來。今則<app type="star" corresp="#1068012"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">太</rdg></app>元帥諸身曼荼羅并諸靈像
<pb n="1069a" xml:id="T55.2163.1069a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1069a01" ed="T"/>所要<note n="1069001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">文＝之【丙】</note><app n="1069001"><lem wit="【大】">文</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">之</rdg></app>書等請來見到。雖云濤波猛<note n="1069002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">沷＝沃【丙】</note><app n="1069002"><lem wit="【大】">沷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">沃</rdg></app>。新
<lb n="1069a02" ed="T"/>羅賊畔。越<note n="1069003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彼＝波【丙】</note><app n="1069003"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">波</rdg></app>厄難平達聖境。是則聖力<note n="1069004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔之〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069004"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="1069a03" ed="T"/>所能也。伏惟皇帝陛下。極德如天。佛日高轉。
<lb n="1069a04" ed="T"/>人之父。佛之化悲群生而濡足。助佛囑而垂
<lb n="1069a05" ed="T"/>衣。以陛下慈育効。祥靈像教希自遠新來。恰
<lb n="1069a06" ed="T"/>似符契。非聖誰測矣。常曉本謂。果三十年經
<lb n="1069a07" ed="T"/>歷漢里。求佛法<note n="1069005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來事＝未事【甲】，來幸【乙】【丙】</note><note n="1069005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">來事＝未事【甲】，＝來幸【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069005"><lem wit="【大】">來。事</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">未事</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">來幸</rdg></app>護國家。而緣唐朝不
<lb n="1069a08" ed="T"/>聽留住。隨使迴歸。竊以一<note n="1069006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">喜＝善【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069006"><lem wit="【大】">喜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">善</rdg></app>此法教生而請
<lb n="1069a09" ed="T"/>來。不任一喜一懼之至。謹附准判官藤原朝
<lb n="1069a10" ed="T"/>臣貞敏。奉表以聞。并請來法門等目錄一<note n="1069007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">通＝道【甲】</note><app n="1069007"><lem wit="【大】">通</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">道</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069a11" ed="T"/>且以奉進。輕黷威嚴伏增戰越。常曉誠恐誠
<lb n="1069a12" ed="T"/>惶謹言。</p>
<lb n="1069a13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069a1301" rend="margin-left:2em">承和六年九月二日入唐學法沙門傳燈
<lb n="1069a14" ed="T"/>大法師位常曉<note place="inline">上表</note>。</p>
<lb n="1069a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069a1501">入唐學法沙門常曉<note n="1069008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔謹言〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069008"><lem wit="【大】">謹言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
<lb n="1069a16" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><cb:mulu level="1" type="其他">上新請來法門并佛像道具事</cb:mulu><head>上新請來法門并佛像<note n="1069009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道具＝等【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069009"><lem wit="【大】">道具</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">等</rdg></app>事</head>
<lb n="1069a17" ed="T"/><list><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a1701"><title>百論疏</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a18" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a1801"><title>三論玄樞</title>一部二卷<note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a19" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a1901"><title>中論三十六門勢疏一卷</title><note place="inline">元康法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a20" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a2001"><title>百論疏略記</title>一部二卷<note place="inline">義持法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a21" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a2101"><title>大佛頂經疏</title>一部六卷<note place="inline">弘抗法師造</note></item>
<lb n="1069a22" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069a2201"><title>大佛頂經<note n="1069010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">玄贊＝略述ィ【原】</note><app n="1069010"><lem wit="【大】">玄贊</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">略述</rdg></app></title>一部三卷<note place="inline">惟<note n="1069011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">慤＝慇【甲】</note><app n="1069011"><lem wit="【大】">慤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慇</rdg></app>法師造</note>
<lb n="1069a23" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069a2301" rend="margin-left:3em">已上六部。依三論宗學頭法師<note n="1069012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">丙本冠註曰等下有脫</note>等
<lb n="1069a24" ed="T"/><note n="1069013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">申＝造【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069013"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">造</rdg></app>求請來。</p>
<lb n="1069a25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069a2501" rend="margin-left:1em">凡如來說稱經。菩薩說稱論。人師說<note n="1069014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">名＝稱【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069014"><lem wit="【大】">名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">稱</rdg></app>疏
<lb n="1069a26" ed="T"/>章<note n="1069015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">傳＋（說說）【丙】</note><app n="1069015"><lem wit="【大】">傳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">傳說說</rdg></app>記等。何以故。唯以佛說經鈍根難解
<lb n="1069a27" ed="T"/>了。是故菩薩作論釋此。最鈍根之<note n="1069016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">類＝賴【甲】</note><app n="1069016"><lem wit="【大】">類</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">賴</rdg></app>。猶
<lb n="1069a28" ed="T"/>未得精旨。因而人師作疏章等。細演經論
<pb n="1069b" xml:id="T55.2163.1069b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1069b01" ed="T"/>之廣旨。於疏師數般。但邪正異耳。今件疏
<lb n="1069b02" ed="T"/>等。釋經論尤微微。解義理<note n="1069017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">絕＝極【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069017"><lem wit="【大】">絕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">極</rdg></app>細細。此土
<lb n="1069b03" ed="T"/>有名彼實未<note n="1069018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">渡＋（論）【甲】</note><app n="1069018"><lem wit="【大】">渡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">渡論</rdg></app>。諸學<note n="1069019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1069019"><lem wit="【大】">徒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">從</rdg></app>等之所疑滯。夫
<lb n="1069b04" ed="T"/>以。百論者。真諦津途。在前以嘉祥寺疏解
<lb n="1069b05" ed="T"/>釋文義。有少不足。今以元康法師疏將定
<lb n="1069b06" ed="T"/>義理也。又空有兩宗論真性理。大佛頂經
<lb n="1069b07" ed="T"/>以為本模。經本雖先來。其疏未有。於義難
<lb n="1069b08" ed="T"/>決。如今以此將正空有兩家諍論義。夫一
<lb n="1069b09" ed="T"/>翼若闕。空行何飛。況乃一乘奧理。義與文
<lb n="1069b10" ed="T"/><note n="1069020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">違＝遠【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1069020"><lem wit="【大】">違</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">遠</rdg></app>。不假疏記微<note n="1069021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">微＝言【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1069021"><lem wit="【大】">微</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">言</rdg></app>無顯。雖有勞載車。<note n="1069022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">冀＝兼【丙】</note><app n="1069022"><lem wit="【大】">冀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">兼</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069b11" ed="T"/>以此俾補乎聖典。</p></item>
<lb n="1069b12" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069b1201"><title>四分律羯磨疏</title>一部四卷<note place="inline">道宣律師撰</note>
<lb n="1069b13" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069b1301" rend="margin-left:3em">已上一部依律宗學頭法師等之覓來。</p>
<lb n="1069b14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069b1401" rend="margin-left:1em">右律羯磨者。眾行手足。佛法壽命也。律家
<lb n="1069b15" ed="T"/>軌則。雖先備來。少有不全。豈非是文乎。然
<lb n="1069b16" ed="T"/>則以<note n="1069023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔此〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069023"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>使補其尸羅闕目。</p></item>
<lb n="1069b17" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069b1701"><title>釋摩訶衍論疏</title>一部三卷<note place="inline">法敏法師造</note>
<lb n="1069b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069b1801" rend="margin-left:3em">已上一部。依真言宗傳法阿闍梨等
<lb n="1069b19" ed="T"/>申求來。</p>
<lb n="1069b20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069b2001" rend="margin-left:1em">右<note n="1069024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔釋〕－【丙】</note><app n="1069024"><lem wit="【大】">釋</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>摩訶衍論者。橫釋顯教。竪括祕藏。
<lb n="1069b21" ed="T"/><note n="1069025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">本＝大【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069025"><lem wit="【大】">本</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">大</rdg></app>論雖先來。左右未定。今以此疏證彼
<lb n="1069b22" ed="T"/>大乘。</p></item>
