<lb n="1069c01" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069c0101"><title>維摩經五教義一卷</title><note place="inline">文<note n="1069035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">襲＝龍【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069035"><lem wit="【大】">襲</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">龍</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#1069029"><lem wit="【大】">禪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>師造</note>
<lb n="1069c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069c0201" rend="margin-left:1em">右維摩經。窮微盡化。妙絕之稱也。造疏之
<lb n="1069c03" ed="T"/>人。數般論旨。左右詞疎。<note n="1069036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB05058"/>塞＝理蹇【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1069036"><lem wit="【大】"><g ref="#CB05058"/>塞</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">理蹇</rdg></app>于是。至開
<lb n="1069c04" ed="T"/>中液公。大宗蕪蔓真<note n="1069037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔極而…提〕四十四字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app cb:word-count="44" n="1069037"><lem wit="【大】">極而開。今見大唐真
<lb n="1069c05" ed="T"/>典近代興盛講文學義之類。總此疏等以
<lb n="1069c06" ed="T"/>為指南。是故每寺講淨名典化度白衣。以
<lb n="1069c07" ed="T"/>液公疏提</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。撕緇<note n="1069038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徒＝從【丙】</note><app n="1069038"><lem wit="【大】">徒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">從</rdg></app>。皆云。雖有<note n="1069039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">論＝諸【甲】</note><app n="1069039"><lem wit="【大】">論</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">諸</rdg></app>師註疏。
<lb n="1069c08" ed="T"/>惠底未足。乍學此文。法鏡轉明。惠燈益照
<lb n="1069c09" ed="T"/><note n="1069040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">者＋（開中道液法師造也）【丙】</note><app n="1069040"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">者開中道液法師造也</rdg></app>。</p></item>
<lb n="1069c10" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069c1001"><title>金剛般若疏</title>一部二卷<note n="1069041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔開中道液法師造也〕－【丙】</note><app n="1069041"><lem wit="【大】"><note place="inline">開中道液法師造<note n="1069042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔也〕－【甲】</note><app n="1069042"><lem wit="【大】">也</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></item>
