<lb n="1069c13" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1069c1301"><title>金剛般若經註一卷</title><note place="inline">南嶽王潔<note n="1069045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔註〕－【丙】</note><app n="1069045"><lem wit="【大】">註</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>
<lb n="1069c14" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1069c1401" rend="margin-left:1em">右疏等。解義妙微行<note n="1069046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耆＝支【甲】，者【乙】【丙】，旨ヵ【丙】</note><note n="1069046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耆＝支【甲】，＝者【乙】【丙】，＝旨ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1069046"><lem wit="【大】"><app><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">耆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">旨</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">支</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">者</rdg></app>那國。此等師疏近
<lb n="1069c15" ed="T"/>代多興。皆以<note n="1069047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">餘＋（餘）【丙】</note><app n="1069047"><lem wit="【大】">餘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">餘餘</rdg></app>師<note n="1069048" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">制＝製ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1069048"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">制</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">製</rdg></app>為傍。以此等疏為
<lb n="1069c16" ed="T"/>正。夫以佛教興轉<note n="1069049" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">依＝以【丙】</note><app n="1069049"><lem wit="【大】">依</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">以</rdg></app>能<note n="1069050" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">宣＋（譜）【甲】【丙】，（譜止）【乙】</note><app n="1069050"><lem wit="【大】">宣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">宣譜</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">宣譜止</rdg></app>人<note n="1069051" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">圻＝垳【丙】</note><app n="1069051"><lem wit="【大】">圻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">垳</rdg></app>古請寄
<lb n="1069c17" ed="T"/>新實。於經本非所改。於義方用相傳<note n="1069052" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">告＝去【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1069052"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">去</rdg></app>
<lb n="1069c18" ed="T"/><note n="1069053" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">耳＝可【丙】</note><app n="1069053"><lem wit="【大】">耳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">可</rdg></app>。</p></item>
