<lb n="1070a09" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070a0901" rend="margin-left:2em">所受學諸尊瑜伽灌頂儀軌等如先渡
<lb n="1070a10" ed="T"/><note n="1070009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">來＝未【丙】</note><app n="1070009"><lem wit="【大】">來</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">未</rdg></app>無殊<note n="1070010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">更＝文【丙】，更＝故ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1070010"><lem wit="【大】"><app><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">更</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">故</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">文</rdg></app>不注之。</p>
<lb n="1070a11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070a1101" rend="margin-left:1em">右顯密之法門。若學得。若未學得。其數不
<lb n="1070a12" ed="T"/>少。唯<note n="1070011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">當代要＝舉未曾【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070011"><lem wit="【大】">當代要</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">舉未曾</rdg></app>有耳。至祕密之宗大體與常
<lb n="1070a13" ed="T"/>無相違。</p></item>
<lb n="1070a14" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a1401"><title>千光<note n="1070012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔王〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】＊</note><app n="1070012"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>佛像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070a1501" rend="margin-left:1em">右恒沙如來有恒沙土。隨其本行得稱各
<lb n="1070a16" ed="T"/>異。唯佛與佛乃所究盡。今千光王佛者。此
<lb n="1070a17" ed="T"/>是觀音本師。其事<note n="1070013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">灼＝歘【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070013"><lem wit="【大】">灼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">歘</rdg></app>然。此像未見。因而
<lb n="1070a18" ed="T"/>請來如件。</p></item>
<lb n="1070a19" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a1901"><title>水月觀世音菩薩像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a20" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070a2001" rend="margin-left:1em">右大悲之用。化形萬方。觀思眾生。拔苦與
<lb n="1070a21" ed="T"/>樂。故示像相使物生信。今見唐朝世人。總
<lb n="1070a22" ed="T"/>以為除災因。天下以為生福緣也。是像此
<lb n="1070a23" ed="T"/>間未流行。故請來如件。</p></item>
<lb n="1070a24" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a2401"><title><note n="1070014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝太【甲】【丙】＊</note><app n="1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥本身將部曼荼羅一鋪</title><note place="inline">總五十餘身</note></item>
<lb n="1070a25" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a2501"><title><app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥大悲身像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070a26" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a2601"><title><app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥忿怒身像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070a27" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070a2701"><title><app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥化身像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070a28" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070a2801" rend="margin-left:1em">右<app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥者。如來之教<note n="1070015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">令＝領【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070015"><lem wit="【大】">令</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">領</rdg></app>輪也。佛為含
<lb n="1070a29" ed="T"/>情作<note n="1070016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">救＝故【丙】</note><app n="1070016"><lem wit="【大】">救</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">故</rdg></app>作護。<note n="1070017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">示＝未【丙】</note><app n="1070017"><lem wit="【大】">示</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">未</rdg></app><app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥形。<note n="1070018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">群＝郡【丙】</note><app n="1070018"><lem wit="【大】">群</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">郡</rdg></app>邪見形
<pb n="1070b" xml:id="T55.2163.1070b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1070b01" ed="T"/>頭破七分。眾惡聽名魔<note n="1070019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道＝通【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070019"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">通</rdg></app>塵散。本經云。
<lb n="1070b02" ed="T"/>佛告阿難。若有國王大臣敬禮誦呪者。其
<lb n="1070b03" ed="T"/>人境<note n="1070020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">土＝世【乙】</note><app n="1070020"><lem wit="【大】">土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">世</rdg></app>。無有惡賊怖難災橫疾疫水旱風
<lb n="1070b04" ed="T"/>霜。國<app type="star" corresp="#1070012"><lem wit="【大】">王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>倍威德。諸民平<note n="1070021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">秦＝泰【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1070021"><lem wit="【大】">秦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">泰</rdg></app>。若有<note n="1070022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔城〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070022"><lem wit="【大】">城</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>邑
<lb n="1070b05" ed="T"/>村落持此<note n="1070023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">經＝法【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070023"><lem wit="【大】">經</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">法</rdg></app>者。莫不蒙利<note n="1070024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">等＝益【丙】</note><app n="1070024"><lem wit="【大】">等</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">益</rdg></app>者。又云。若
<lb n="1070b06" ed="T"/>國土<note n="1070025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">襄＝衰【甲】【乙】，襄禍＝褰<g ref="#CB02932"/>【丙】</note><note n="1070025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">襄禍＝褰<g ref="#CB02932"/>【丙】，襄＝衰【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070025"><lem wit="【大】">襄禍</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">褰<g ref="#CB02932"/></rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">衰禍</rdg></app>。雨<note n="1070026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">澤＝降【丙】</note><app n="1070026"><lem wit="【大】">澤</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">降</rdg></app>不調。以此<app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥呪安
<lb n="1070b07" ed="T"/>四<note n="1070027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔城〕－【乙】</note><app n="1070027"><lem wit="【大】">城</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>門上。即得風雨順時。將鎮國<note n="1070028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">土＝上【丙】</note><app n="1070028"><lem wit="【大】">土</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">上</rdg></app>。四
<lb n="1070b08" ed="T"/>方隣歒不起逆心等者。然則如法行。國長
<lb n="1070b09" ed="T"/><note n="1070029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">存＝在【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070029"><lem wit="【大】">存</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">在</rdg></app>安寧。剎那<note n="1070030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">婦＝歸【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1070030"><lem wit="【大】">婦</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">歸</rdg></app>人<note n="1070031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">固＝同【甲】【乙】，目【丙】</note><note n="1070031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">固＝同【甲】【乙】，＝目【丙】</note><app n="1070031"><lem wit="【大】">固</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">同</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">目</rdg></app>得十利不可思議
<lb n="1070b10" ed="T"/>也。大元帥之力。今見唐朝皆依此為治國
<lb n="1070b11" ed="T"/>之<note n="1070032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＝實ィ【甲】</note><app n="1070032"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】" type="variantRemark">實</rdg></app>。勝歒之要。<note n="1070033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">是＝見【丙】</note><app n="1070033"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">見</rdg></app>以定自在王菩薩偈
<lb n="1070b12" ed="T"/>讚曰。我聞元帥名。世間救苦厄。一切<note n="1070034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">大＝厄【甲】</note><app n="1070034"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">厄</rdg></app>
<lb n="1070b13" ed="T"/>神中。奇特無有<note n="1070035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">比＝此【丙】</note><app n="1070035"><lem wit="【大】">比</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">此</rdg></app>。種種變化身。而拔眾
<lb n="1070b14" ed="T"/>生苦。我今聞往昔。<note n="1070036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">寶＝實【丙】</note><app n="1070036"><lem wit="【大】">寶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">實</rdg></app>不可思議。</p>
<lb n="1070b15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070b1501" rend="margin-left:1em">此法也。吾朝不多流行。以是略<note n="1070037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">要＝案【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070037"><lem wit="【大】">要</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">案</rdg></app>法儀圖
<lb n="1070b16" ed="T"/>像請求。息災招福無比<note n="1070038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（此）＋法【丙】</note><app n="1070038"><lem wit="【大】">法</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">此法</rdg></app>。誰非歸依耶。</p></item>
<lb n="1070b17" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070b1701"><title>大聖千臂千頭金毘羅童子像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070b1801" rend="margin-left:1em">右金毘羅童子者。此釋迦之化現也。經云。
<lb n="1070b19" ed="T"/>佛在歡喜園中為諸眾生說法。是時外道
<lb n="1070b20" ed="T"/>波旬起諸惡障。令諸眾生受大苦惱。爾時
<lb n="1070b21" ed="T"/>如來密化自身作金毘羅童子。調伏外道
<lb n="1070b22" ed="T"/>諸魔。於惡世中饒益眾生。此法也尤鎮國
<lb n="1070b23" ed="T"/>利物之寶。法力之奇特也不思議。此像并
<lb n="1070b24" ed="T"/>法儀。持明者所祕。本<note n="1070039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">朝＝猶【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070039"><lem wit="【大】">朝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">猶</rdg></app>未見。請來如件。</p></item>
<lb n="1070b25" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070b2501"><title><note n="1070040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔大聖〕－【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1070040"><lem wit="【大】">大聖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>六童子像一<note n="1070041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軀＝鋪【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070041"><lem wit="【大】">軀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">鋪</rdg></app></title>
<lb n="1070b26" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070b2601" rend="margin-left:1em">右六童子者。經云。竝是過去諸佛之所化
<lb n="1070b27" ed="T"/>身。為救護一切有情故。若有國土作此法
<lb n="1070b28" ed="T"/>者。即至而現其身護國利人等者。今見唐
<lb n="1070b29" ed="T"/>朝世人。多修此法。其力見奧。是靈像此間
<lb n="1070b30" ed="T"/>未有流行。因而請來。其修行之<note n="1070042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">儀亦甚＝像亦其【乙】，儀示甚【丙】</note><note n="1070042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">儀亦甚＝像亦其【乙】，＝儀示甚【丙】</note><app n="1070042"><lem wit="【大】">儀。亦甚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">像亦其</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">儀示甚</rdg></app>
<pb n="1070c" xml:id="T55.2163.1070c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1070c01" ed="T"/><note n="1070043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（不）＋疎【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070043"><lem wit="【大】">疎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">不疎</rdg></app>略。</p></item>
<lb n="1070c02" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070c0201"><title>大聖迦毘羅神王像一<note n="1070044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">軀＋（一軀）【丙】</note><app n="1070044"><lem wit="【大】">軀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">軀一軀</rdg></app></title>
<lb n="1070c03" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070c0301" rend="margin-left:1em">右神者。此是如來化身。秦代羅什三藏。昔
<lb n="1070c04" ed="T"/>周五天感得此神相隨送來。今見唐中皆
<lb n="1070c05" ed="T"/>貴此神為<note n="1070045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">權＝擁【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1070045"><lem wit="【大】">權</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">擁</rdg></app>法護國之憑若有病人稱名
<lb n="1070c06" ed="T"/>即除。貧窮之人依願必富。靈驗見顯。無有
<lb n="1070c07" ed="T"/>一人不歸依者。夫佛化從西東流。應時利
<lb n="1070c08" ed="T"/>物。豈非如來<note n="1070046" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">未＝來【甲】【丙】，〔未〕ィ－【乙】</note><app n="1070046"><lem wit="【大】">未</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">來</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】" type="variantRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>化乎。</p></item>
<lb n="1070c09" ed="T"/><note n="1070047" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔三光…甚可軌也〕百八十五字－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app cb:word-count="185" n="1070047"><lem wit="【大】"><item xml:id="itemT55p1070c0901"><title>三光天子像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1070c10" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070c1001"><title>二十八宿像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070c1101" rend="margin-left:1em">右三光者日月五星名七耀。四四方七星
<lb n="1070c12" ed="T"/>合二十八宿此土之人唯聞名見光。未知
<lb n="1070c13" ed="T"/>其形量。今此耀宿之形像尤祕尤密。實有
<lb n="1070c14" ed="T"/>靈驗。唐國猶不多傳。況乎日朝所未曾見。
<lb n="1070c15" ed="T"/>但陰陽師等意推作像。以傳式用是不契
<lb n="1070c16" ed="T"/>當耳。今所請像各有可軌也。</p></item>
<lb n="1070c17" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070c1701"><title>聖者菩提王像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070c1801" rend="margin-left:1em">右菩提王者。大唐山神也。潤州樓山有一
<lb n="1070c19" ed="T"/>比丘。修練禪業現感此神現形表靈受戒
<lb n="1070c20" ed="T"/>修道故名菩提王。隨人祈請加護成願。遂
<lb n="1070c21" ed="T"/>為國鎮人歸也。因茲處處作像人人尊重
<lb n="1070c22" ed="T"/>親見其事甚可軌也。</p></item></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>
<lb n="1070c23" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1070c2301"><title>深沙神王像一軀</title>
<lb n="1070c24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1070c2401" rend="margin-left:1em">右唐代玄奘三藏遠涉五天感得此神。此
<lb n="1070c25" ed="T"/>是北方多聞天王化身也。今唐國人總重
<pb n="1071a" xml:id="T55.2163.1071a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1071a01" ed="T"/>此神救災成益。其驗現前。無有一人不依
<lb n="1071a02" ed="T"/>行者。寺裏人家皆在此神。<note n="1071001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">自見＝目【乙】</note><app n="1071001"><lem wit="【大】">自見</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">目</rdg></app>靈驗實不
<lb n="1071a03" ed="T"/>思議。具事如記文。請來如件。</p></item>
<lb n="1071a04" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1071a0401"><title>菩薩像一軀</title></item>
<lb n="1071a05" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1071a0501"><title><note n="1071002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此前行甲乙丙三本俱有七曜二十八宿形像八字</note>護摩爐壇樣一十五種</title>
<lb n="1071a06" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071a0601" rend="margin-left:1em">右像唐朝示現。其靈驗奧也。人舉歸。息災
<lb n="1071a07" ed="T"/>增福無<note n="1071003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">過＝邊【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1071003"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">邊</rdg></app>此者。具事如記文。請來如件。</p>
<lb n="1071a08" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071a0801" rend="margin-left:1em">夫至道無言。非言不顯。真際絕形。待形乃
<lb n="1071a09" ed="T"/>悟。絕形者是真如三寶。示形者其住持三
<lb n="1071a10" ed="T"/>寶也。如來本願順機變相。大聖慈悲應時
<lb n="1071a11" ed="T"/>濟物。經云。應以佛身得度者。即現佛身。乃
<lb n="1071a12" ed="T"/>至八部身得度者。即皆現之而為說法等
<lb n="1071a13" ed="T"/>也。凡<note n="1071004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔正〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071004"><lem wit="【大】">正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>法之世。魔伴<note n="1071005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">無＝立【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071005"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">立</rdg></app>威。<note n="1071006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔所以佛〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071006"><lem wit="【大】">所以佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app><note n="1071007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">化＝陀ヵ【甲】【乙】</note><app n="1071007"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">化</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】" type="correctionRemark">陀</rdg></app>
<lb n="1071a14" ed="T"/>多住慈悲。像末之時。邪<note n="1071008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">使＝便【甲】，使競興＝法【丙】</note><note n="1071008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">使競興＝法【丙】，使＝便【甲】</note><app n="1071008"><lem wit="【大】">使競興</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">法</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">便競興</rdg></app>。所以如
<lb n="1071a15" ed="T"/>來。多形忿怒。佛力如是。實鎮國利人之寶
<lb n="1071a16" ed="T"/>也。受持頂戴。福利無極。外以摧魔軍。內以
<lb n="1071a17" ed="T"/>調伏煩惱。諸佛智悲如此。</p></item></list></cb:div>
