<lb n="1071a25" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1071a2501"><title>金剛<note n="1071009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">海＝界【丙】</note><app n="1071009"><lem wit="【大】">海</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">界</rdg></app>三十七尊種子曼荼羅一<note n="1071010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔面〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071010"><lem wit="【大】">面</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></title></item>
