<lb n="1071a27" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1071a2701"><title><note n="1071012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（西天…條）九字∞（西天…面）六字【甲】</note><note n="1071012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（西天供養白疊巾一條）九字∞（西天檀褥一面）六字【甲】</note><app n="1071012"><lem wit="【大】">西天供養白疊巾一條</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">西天檀褥一面</rdg></app></title></item>
