<lb n="1071a29" ed="T"/><item xml:id="itemT55p1071a2901"><title>傳法阿闍梨授弟子灌頂法二卷</title>
<pb n="1071b" xml:id="T55.2163.1071b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="1071b01" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071b0101" rend="margin-left:1em">右道具。竝栖靈寺阿闍梨之所<note n="1071014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔傳〕－【甲】</note><app n="1071014"><lem wit="【大】">傳</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>付也。</p>
<lb n="1071b02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071b0201">常曉去承和五年仲夏之月。<note n="1071015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔隨入唐〕－【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071015"><lem wit="【大】">隨入唐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>判官
<lb n="1071b03" ed="T"/><note n="1071016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔菅〕－【丙】，菅＝藤ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1071016"><lem wit="【大】"><app><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">菅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">藤</rdg></app></lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>原朝臣善主。同上<note n="1071017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">第四舶發＝弟【丙】</note><app n="1071017"><lem wit="【大】">第四舶發</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">弟</rdg></app><note n="1071018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">赴＝起【丙】</note><app n="1071018"><lem wit="【大】">赴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">起</rdg></app><note n="1071019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">尸＝支【甲】</note><app n="1071019"><lem wit="【大】">尸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">支</rdg></app>那。
<lb n="1071b04" ed="T"/>其<note n="1071020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔年〕－【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071020"><lem wit="【大】">年</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>六月到揚州著岸。八月下<note n="1071021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">旬＝句【丙】</note><app n="1071021"><lem wit="【大】">旬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">句</rdg></app>到淮南
<lb n="1071b05" ed="T"/>大都督府廣<note n="1071022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">綾＝凌【丙】</note><app n="1071022"><lem wit="【大】">綾</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">凌</rdg></app>舘安置。同年十二月住栖靈
<lb n="1071b06" ed="T"/>寺大悲持念院。隨同寺灌頂阿闍梨文㻮和
<lb n="1071b07" ed="T"/>尚。并華林寺三教講論大德元照座主。顯密
<lb n="1071b08" ed="T"/>兩法頗以兼習。六年正月四日設<note n="1071023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">二＝一【丙】</note><app n="1071023"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">一</rdg></app><note n="1071024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">百＝日【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071024"><lem wit="【大】">百</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】【丙】">日</rdg></app>僧
<lb n="1071b09" ed="T"/>齋。普供四眾。於此日諸寺大德綱維竝臨齋
<lb n="1071b10" ed="T"/>會應供隨喜。常曉夜就師邊受學瑜伽。<note n="1071025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">晝＝盡【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071025"><lem wit="【大】">晝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">盡</rdg></app>周
<lb n="1071b11" ed="T"/>諸寺<note n="1071026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">覓＝不見【丙】</note><app n="1071026"><lem wit="【大】">覓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">不見</rdg></app><note n="1071027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">問＝向【丙】</note><app n="1071027"><lem wit="【大】">問</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">向</rdg></app>法門。則喚<note n="1071028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔即〕－ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1071028"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>供奉李<note n="1071029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">全＝金【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071029"><lem wit="【大】">全</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">金</rdg></app>等圖
<lb n="1071b12" ed="T"/>繪<app type="star" corresp="#1070014"><lem wit="【大】">大</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">太</rdg></app>元帥<note n="1071030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">將＝大ィ【原】</note><app n="1071030"><lem wit="【大】">將</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【原】" type="variantRemark">大</rdg></app>部曼荼羅等諸尊像。并寫文
<lb n="1071b13" ed="T"/>書。漸有次第。二月十九日受傳法阿闍梨位
<lb n="1071b14" ed="T"/>灌頂。於此日設大齋普供大眾。留後判官藤
<lb n="1071b15" ed="T"/>原朝臣貞敏。別<note n="1071031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔請丹墀〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071031"><lem wit="【大】">請丹墀</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>真人高主知乘安墀
<lb n="1071b16" ed="T"/>宿禰<note n="1071032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔良棟〕－【丙】</note><app n="1071032"><lem wit="【大】">良棟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>等。<note n="1071033" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">同＝聞【丙】</note><app n="1071033"><lem wit="【大】">同</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">聞</rdg></app>臨道場。拋花定本尊。受五
<lb n="1071b17" ed="T"/>智灌頂。二十一日准勅離州却赴本朝。常曉
<lb n="1071b18" ed="T"/>本業三論之枝。兼真言之條。而才能不聞。言
<lb n="1071b19" ed="T"/>無取。逢時<note n="1071034" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">之人＝乏人【甲】，乏入【乙】</note><note n="1071034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之人＝乏人【甲】，＝乏入【乙】</note><app n="1071034"><lem wit="【大】">之人</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">乏人</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">乏入</rdg></app><note n="1071035" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">簉＝選ヵ【丙】</note><app n="1071035"><lem resp="Taisho" wit="【大】">簉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】" type="correctionRemark">選</rdg></app>留學<note n="1071036" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">員＝真【乙】，貞【丙】</note><note n="1071036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">員＝真【乙】，＝貞【丙】</note><app n="1071036"><lem wit="【大】">員</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【乙】">真</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">貞</rdg></app>限以三十年。尋
<lb n="1071b20" ed="T"/>以一乘。任重人<note n="1071037" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">弱＝溺【丙】</note><app n="1071037"><lem wit="【大】">弱</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">溺</rdg></app>。夙夜懃<note n="1071038" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">愿＝慇【甲】</note><app n="1071038"><lem wit="【大】">愿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">慇</rdg></app>。雖然國命難
<lb n="1071b21" ed="T"/>乖<note n="1071039" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">忘＝忌【丙】</note><app n="1071039"><lem wit="【大】">忘</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">忌</rdg></app><note n="1071040" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">親＝視【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071040"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">視</rdg></app>萬里住<note n="1071041" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">心＝止【丙】</note><app n="1071041"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">止</rdg></app>遠境。且頗受學顯密兩
<lb n="1071b22" ed="T"/>道。比未見及太<note n="1071042" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">知＝和【甲】【乙】【丙】</note><app n="1071042"><lem wit="【大】">知</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】【丙】">和</rdg></app>有勅不聽<note n="1071043" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">留＝㽜【丙】</note><app n="1071043"><lem wit="【大】">留</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">㽜</rdg></app>住。<note n="1071044" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">（因）＋而【甲】【丙】</note><app n="1071044"><lem wit="【大】">而</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【丙】">因而</rdg></app>隨使
<lb n="1071b23" ed="T"/>却迴。少間所成<note n="1071045" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">此＝些些【甲】【乙】，此＋（此）【丙】</note><app n="1071045"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】【乙】">些些</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【丙】">此此</rdg></app>法儀注顯如件。</p>
<lb n="1071b24" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071b2401" rend="margin-left:1em">承和六年九月五日。</p>
<lb n="1071b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT55p1071b2501" rend="margin-left:3em">入唐學法沙門傳燈大法師位常曉上。</p></item></list></cb:div>
